{"tid":232410,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭秀文孖Mark嫂探望 Kay餵人奶未收身","createTime":"2017-05-06T17:18:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T21:06:10.000Z","uid":22609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca494367e2bf3921b5493df9494239fd159ff37f","tid":232410,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/07/011649_e9475ec8a8ef53d0cf3d7597acb80f77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F07%2F011649_e9475ec8a8ef53d0cf3d7597acb80f77.jpg&h=db94d617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/74qXO64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F74qXO64.jpg&h=12ea941d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pbk4y4x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpbk4y4x.jpg&h=16392db9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄭秀文（Sammi）昨日孖住雷頌德（Mark）太太梁家玉，到大埔探謝安琪（Kay）和B女張靖（Karina）。只見Sammi笑得好開心，並以純熟手勢抱住Karina，而Kay就肥嘟嘟未收身。Kay強調呢刻覺得身體健康最緊要，加上要餵母乳，所以唔減肥住，連老公張繼聰都贊成！<br />\n<br />\n        謝安琪（Kay）細女Karina早前已滿月，有女萬事足的她現時在家專心湊女，亦冇講幾時復出。而Sammi和梁家玉昨日好有心一齊去探她們，張繼聰指Kay和Sammi是好朋友，他更讚Sammi是一個很有愛的人，而Mark嫂因為是鄰居，所以成為好友。<br />\n<br />\n　　對於太太Kay未收身，張繼聰認為生完BB，坐月時最緊要是健康，身形可以好有彈性。一講到囡囡，張繼聰就開心到見牙唔見眼。只見相中的Karina樣子可愛，睡覺時十分惹人喜愛，看來以湊女為樂的Kay，要隔多一段時間才能復出工作了。<br />\n<br />\n本報記者　網上圖片<br />\n<br />\nSource: 頭條日報 <a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/ent/563846/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fent%2F563846%2F&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725Bv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=1c0fff35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fent%2F563846%2F&h=c24f4111\" target=\"_blank\">hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/ent/563846/</a>"},{"pid":"deda4f1d4be369bb8ff39f613e3c4447bc6f032d","tid":232410,"uid":111789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:25:45.000Z","msg":"謝生就好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 晚晚又有人奶飲"},{"pid":"99705185c88b94b66325c4d86e4148390fde3221","tid":232410,"uid":40940,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:27:54.000Z","msg":"謝安琪正中整容眼<br />\n一落妝就好恐怖"},{"pid":"6605f0da3e740a4f0e683cb93f86230d8eb3e523","tid":232410,"uid":269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T18:03:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>謝安琪正中整容眼<br />\n一落妝就好恐怖</blockquote><br />\n收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"121cf97488e220c14f38107cb9a724d2ba8d4fb6","tid":232410,"uid":35296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T18:52:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>謝安琪正中整容眼<br />\n一落妝就好恐怖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b9b7d0d3e2e93d47572aa71fb5e9e1eb71f29a","tid":232410,"uid":65144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:06:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>謝安琪正中整容眼<br />\n一落妝就好恐怖</blockquote><br />\n謝安琪真係大器晚成個d人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成4張野真係老蚌生珠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n謝生重要後生過技安琪，我係謝生實出去偷食食返d廿幾三十頭平衡下心理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d23c9a0a0d0c748434d4efa927b37ff0cbe54aeb","tid":232410,"uid":70629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:19:25.000Z","msg":"Kay BB <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3cf6a3a67238f9e811b341473663ed49670a260","tid":232410,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:24:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Kay BB <img src=\"/assets/fac